 Sales Analysis Dashboard

This project is a Power BI dashboard to analyze sales performance.

Tools Used
- Power BI
- SQL
- Python

 Dashboard Overview
![Dashboard](screenshots/dashboard.png)

Shows overall sales performance including total revenue, trends, and top customers.

 Sales Trend
![Trend](screenshots/sales_trend.png)

 Displays monthly sales trends and peak periods.

 Top Customers
![Customers](screenshots/top_customers.png)

 Highlights top 10 customers by revenue.

 Sales by Region
![Region](screenshots/region_analysis.png)

SQL queries used for data analysis (sql/analysis.sql)

Python script used for data cleaning (python/data_cleaning.py)
